<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 23 Dec 2023 00:50:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>安哥拉退出欧佩克为更多中国投资开辟道路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/angolas-opec-exit-opens-way-more-chinese-investment-2023-12-22/</link><description>石油占安哥拉出口的 90%，该国正在寻求经济多元化，但也需要收入。 “中国是一个举足轻重且经过验证的合作伙伴，”其外交部长表示。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 15:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/angolas-opec-exit-opens-way-more-chinese-investment-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾副总统领跑者表示，我们不会让与中国发生战争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/we-wont-let-there-be-war-with-china-taiwan-vp-frontrunner-says-2023-12-22/</link><description>台北前驻美国最高外交官、现任台湾下一任副总统的领跑者周五表示，台湾执政党不会让与中国爆发战争，但挑起紧张局势的罪魁祸首是中国。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 13:46:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/we-wont-let-there-be-war-with-china-taiwan-vp-frontrunner-says-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>国航计划配股至多8.42亿美元购买飞机以增加资本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-china-plans-up-842-mln-share-placement-buy-planes-boost-capital-2023-12-22/</link><description>中国国际航空公司周五表示，计划在上海证券交易所通过非公开发行股票筹集至多60亿元人民币（8.42亿美元），以扩大机队规模并补充营运资金。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 13:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-china-plans-up-842-mln-share-placement-buy-planes-boost-capital-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>晨竞：史诗般的圣诞老人集会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2023-12-22/</link><description>阿曼达·库珀 (Amanda Cooper) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 11:03:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>尽管美中军事对话恢复，台湾和南中国海仍隐现危险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-schina-sea-loom-dangers-despite-revived-us-china-military-dialogue-2023-12-22/</link><description>中国和亚洲分析人士表示，中美之间恢复军事对话可能有助于缓解部分紧张局势，但台湾和南中国海问题上的根本分歧仍然存在，成为危险的潜在爆发点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 10:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-schina-sea-loom-dangers-despite-revived-us-china-military-dialogue-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪将在匈牙利建设新能源汽车生产基地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-build-new-energy-vehicle-production-base-hungary-2023-12-22/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周五表示，将在匈牙利建设新能源汽车生产基地。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 08:51:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-build-new-energy-vehicle-production-base-hungary-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国吉利警告红海袭击将推迟欧洲电动汽车发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-warns-red-sea-attacks-delay-europe-bound-ev-shipments-2023-12-22/</link><description>中国汽车制造商吉利周五警告称，由于红海“局势”，也门武装分子正在袭击船只，迫使托运人采取更长、更昂贵的航线，其电动汽车销售可能会受到交付延迟的影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 08:36:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-warns-red-sea-attacks-delay-europe-bound-ev-shipments-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾与加拿大签署具有里程碑意义的双边投资协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-signs-landmark-bilateral-investment-agreement-with-canada-2023-12-22/</link><description>台湾和加拿大周五签署了双边投资协议，推动了台湾政府加强与志同道合的民主伙伴的商业关系的努力，并可能为台湾加入一项重要的泛太平洋贸易协定提供便利。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 08:01:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-signs-landmark-bilateral-investment-agreement-with-canada-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>土地所有者投诉后，中国公司被禁止瓦努阿图原木出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-firm-barred-vanuatu-log-exports-after-landowner-complaints-2023-12-22/</link><description>当地居民表示，在最近的政治动荡期间，一家中国公司开始在瓦努阿图进行伐木活动，这引发了人们对这个太平洋岛国的环境和穿着军装的工人的担忧，而北京和华盛顿正在争夺影响力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 07:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-firm-barred-vanuatu-log-exports-after-landowner-complaints-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉获得上海土地用于大型电池工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tesla-launches-shanghai-megapack-battery-project-chinese-state-media-2023-12-22/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周五报道，特斯拉已在上海购买了一座大型电池制造工厂的土地，预计将于 2024 年第四季度开始生产。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 04:22:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tesla-launches-shanghai-megapack-battery-project-chinese-state-media-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>波音自2019年以来首架交付中国的梦想客机抵达</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeings-first-dreamliner-delivery-china-since-2019-land-friday-2023-12-22/</link><description>波音公司自 2019 年以来首架直接向中国交付的 787 梦想客机于周五在上海降落，此举可能会加速结束中国对该公司盈利的 737 MAX 交付已冻结四年多的局面。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 04:20:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeings-first-dreamliner-delivery-china-since-2019-land-friday-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国宣布减少视频游戏支出的规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issues-draft-rules-online-game-management-2023-12-22/</link><description>中国监管机构周五宣布了一系列旨在限制鼓励电子游戏的支出和奖励的规定，这对今年恢复增长的全球最大游戏市场造成了打击。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 04:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issues-draft-rules-online-game-management-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国气温攀升，刺骨的寒冷放松了控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/biting-cold-loosen-grip-temperatures-creep-higher-china-2023-12-22/</link><description>寒潮席卷中国大部分地区，带来近两周零度以下的天气，从周末开始，一轮暖空气将开始从中国北部向南部流动，气温将升高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 04:08:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/biting-cold-loosen-grip-temperatures-creep-higher-china-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院驳回撤销黎智英煽动叛乱指控的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-rejects-bid-drop-sedition-charge-against-jimmy-lai-2023-12-22/</link><description>香港一家法院周五驳回了法律团队要求撤销对民主大亨黎智英煽动叛乱指控的请求。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 03:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-rejects-bid-drop-sedition-charge-against-jimmy-lai-2023-12-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商将反抗巨大的脱钩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/breakingviews/chinas-automakers-will-defy-great-uncoupling-2023-12-22/</link><description>中美大脱钩已成为不言而喻的事实。在从微芯片到电信设备等战略敏感领域，两个超级大国之间已经产生了分歧。但汽车公司 — — 特别是电动汽车 — — 可以勾勒出美国保护主义的界限。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 01:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/breakingviews/chinas-automakers-will-defy-great-uncoupling-2023-12-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>